tion-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">宋莹老师从中学时期开始自学快速阅读、快速记忆和思维导图技术。高考时，以所在城市政治科第一名的成绩，考入广东外语外贸大学就读企业管理专业。</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">这让她第一次体会到脑力开发技术的神奇。</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span><img title=".png" alt="timg7.png" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAgMOhLAh7481/image/ueditor/79493400_1536228222.png"/></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">她在04年一次偶然的机会中结识了中国首两位世界记忆大师：张杰老师和王茂华老师。并就很快投入到了自己非常感兴趣的脑力开发训练中。</span><strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">读完大学二年级，她就成为广外罕有的停学学生。决定停学一年时间，全身心的从事脑力开发的教学与推广。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><img title="https://static-1253442168.image.myqcloud.com/cover_img/cover_38911089_966d94f5dcce2ab5ead45689cf4f91e4.jpg" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" alt="https://static-1253442168.image.myqcloud.com/cover_img/cover_38911089_966d94f5dcce2ab5ead45689cf4f91e4.jpg" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAgMOhLAh7481/image/ueditor/1185800_1536228223.jpg"/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">当时与宋老师共同在广州中科院做脑力教学的同事还有郭传威（后来中国首届记忆力竞标赛冠军）、郭玉峰（中国首届记忆力竞标赛亚军）、车伟坚（中国首届记忆力竞标赛季军）、刘平（世界记忆力单项冠军）、陈玉娟（世界记忆力单项冠军）、庄海湛（世界记忆大师）等多位我国脑力开发的核心推动者。</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">在广州中科院培训基地的教学过程中，培养了大量10-80岁的优秀的学员：</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><img title="https://static-1253442168.image.myqcloud.com/cover_img/cover_38911089_757b2cc7aa9ff2a85284b895ae7a1428.jpg" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" alt="https://static-1253442168.image.myqcloud.com/cover_img/cover_38911089_757b2cc7aa9ff2a85284b895ae7a1428.jpg" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAgMOhLAh7481/image/ueditor/35058900_1536228223.jpg"/></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">就在这一年，她在广州各大高效巡回演讲了超过30场。其中包括中山大学、广东外语外贸大学、华南理工大学、华南师范大学、华南农业大学等等。</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">在广外演讲的时候，同班同学也因这次偶遇而感到非常惊讶。</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">之后，她顺利完成最后两年的大学课程，并获得优秀毕业论文奖。</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">期间，<strong>在她和同事的共同努力下，培养出超过10位世界记忆大师。</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">2010年，宋莹老师开始在北京各大高校巡回演讲。参加面授课程的学员来自北京大学、人民大学、北京外语学院、北京理工、中央团校等等各所高校。</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">这使得越来越多天资聪慧的高校学生，开始关注自脑力开发，并燃起了参与脑力开发事业的兴趣。到现在为止，已经有多位学员成长为优秀的老师。</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><img title="https://static-1253442168.image.myqcloud.com/cover_img/cover_38911089_ae597a4caa6af0fee18aeb9d350de0ea.jpg" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" alt="https://static-1253442168.image.myqcloud.com/cover_img/cover_38911089_ae597a4caa6af0fee18aeb9d350de0ea.jpg" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAgMOhLAh7481/image/ueditor/72493600_1536228223.jpg"/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">于此同时，</span><strong><span style="font-size: 14px;">从2009年开始宋老师也面向企业进行思维导图内训。</span><span style="font-size: 14px;">授课对象包括：广州移动、佛山移动、东莞移动、河北电网、聚成华商书院、羊城晚报金羊网、无限极总公司、和悦社会服务、乾坤福酒业、格正文化、康展文化、交大书香社广州部、和善玻璃、科德技术等等。</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><img title="https://static-1253442168.image.myqcloud.com/cover_img/cover_38911089_3b6fe7cb81b1e315ac24ea91e00d433c.jpg" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" alt="https://static-1253442168.image.myqcloud.com/cover_img/cover_38911089_3b6fe7cb81b1e315ac24ea91e00d433c.jpg" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAgMOhLAh7481/image/ueditor/9184100_1536228224.jpg"/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><img title="https://static-1253442168.image.myqcloud.com/cover_img/cover_38911089_d1fd40e95f62283d087f1401d81f68ae.jpg" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" alt="https://static-1253442168.image.myqcloud.com/cover_img/cover_38911089_d1fd40e95f62283d087f1401d81f68ae.jpg" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAgMOhLAh7481/image/ueditor/31168400_1536228224.jpg"/></p><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: center; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding-left: 1em; padding-right: 1em; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="display: inline-block; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; border-radius: 0.5em; background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">课程须知</p></span> </section><section style="border: 1px solid rgb(192, 200, 209); margin-top: -1em; padding: 20px 10px 10px; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239); box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.2; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">1、 内容包括八节共32个视频PPT课。可反复不限次回听。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">2、 敬请理解：线上课程为虚拟产品，订阅成功后无法退订、转让。</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br/></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><p><br/></p>

第一节 职场思维导图入门5：成长过程

