 text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><p><br/></p>

第三节 思维导图记忆法2：记住思维导图的五大方法

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appc3vFlthQ9175/v_5b90fd2fe2f2d_K6wP5Se1

<p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; text-align: left;">生命大部分时间会用来工作，每个人都希望自己能力更强，效率更高，创造更多财富。提升自己必不可少。与其盲目的延长工作时间，不如关注思维模式的升级。这是撬动生命的绝佳支点。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">如何根本改变低效阅读的习惯？<br/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">如何做到一天阅读3本书籍？</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">如何掌握快速提分的学习方法？</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">如何轻松进行全局策划和项目管理？</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">如何高效进行创业规划？</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">八节PPT视频课程将让我们打开新的天地</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">（适合18岁以上学员学习）</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><img title=".png" alt="适合人群_自定义px_2018.05.14.png" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAgMOhLAh7481/image/ueditor/60255700_1536228219.png"/></span>&nbsp;</span><br/></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><img title="https://static-1253442168.image.myqcloud.com/cover_img/cover_38911089_7b9160c152694f5788e904918f6b38db.jpg" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;" alt="https://static-1253442168.image.myqcloud.com/cover_img/cover_38911089_7b9160c152694f5788e904918f6b38db.jpg" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAgMOhLAh7481/image/ueditor/79546700_1536228219.jpg"/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">思维导图是一种记录发散思维的笔记工具，它也是一种新的思维模式。</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">它充分利用了左右脑的功能。长期使用可以提升分析能力、全局统筹能力、想象力和记忆力。</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><img title="https://static-1253442168.image.myqcloud.com/cover_